page.title: 11A TYPICAL FRIDAY
page.content: My name is Heather. I wake at 7.30 am and read a book till 8.00 am. I then get up and get washed and dressed and go for breakfast. I have a cup of tea and a slice of toast. I put all my books in my bag and then go out the door. I arrive at school about 8.45 am. I then play with Claire. I get into{school}at 9.00 am. We do our test. Our marks say where we sit. It is break at 10.30. I go out and do cartwheels with Claire. It is lunchtime at 1230 pm and we finish and we finish at 3.15 pm. I go home and watch{TV}and at 6.45 go to{Girl {Guides.}We finish at 9.00 pm and I go to bed between 9.30 and 9.45 pm. ?1002 06080222
